methods.getMemoKey:
Produces a MemoKey for this aggregation state factory.

 If two AggregationStateFactories have equal memoKeys, then Table.by(io.deephaven.db.v2.by.AggregationStateFactory, io.deephaven.db.v2.select.SelectColumn...) operations that have the same
 group by columns may be memoized.  In that case instead of recomputing the result; the original result will be
 used.
If null is returned, the operation will not be memoized.

:return: (io.deephaven.db.v2.by.AggregationMemoKey) an AggregationMemoKey, null if this operation can not be memoized.
